sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Client Widget<br/>(Browser)
    participant S as Server<br/>(Cloud Run)
    participant G as Gemini Live API<br/>(Vertex AI)

    Note over U,G: 1. Voice Conversation

    U->>C: "Hey, what can you help me with?"
    C->>S: Audio stream (WebSocket)
    S->>G: Forward audio
    G-->>S: "I can help you navigate this site..."
    S->>S: Wav2Arkit ONNX (CPU)<br/>Audio → 52 Blendshapes
    S-->>C: sync_frame (Audio + Blendshapes @ 30 FPS)
    C->>U: Avatar speaks with lip-sync
    U->>C: "Actually wait—"
    C->>S: interrupt
    S->>G: Cancel current response
    G-->>S: (stops generating)

    Note over U,G: 2. Screen Awareness

    U->>C: "What do you see on my screen?"
    C->>S: Audio stream
    S->>G: Forward audio
    G-->>S: tool_call: request_screen_context
    S-->>C: Capture viewport
    C->>C: html2canvas → screenshot
    C->>S: Screenshot (base64)
    S->>G: Image → Gemini Vision
    G-->>S: "I can see a product listing page with sneakers..."
    S-->>C: sync_frame (Audio + Blendshapes)
    C->>U: Avatar describes the page

    Note over U,G: 3. Action Taking

    U->>C: "Find me the pricing section"
    C->>S: Audio stream
    S->>G: Forward audio
    G-->>S: tool_call: navigate_to_section("pricing")
    S-->>C: Scroll to #pricing
    C->>C: Page scrolls to pricing section
    G-->>S: "Here's the pricing section, let me show you a comparison..."
    G-->>S: tool_call: send_rich_content(comparison table)
    S-->>C: Render table in chat
    S-->>C: sync_frame (Audio + Blendshapes)
    C->>U: Avatar explains pricing with lip-sync
